casebody.data:
Russell BUCKLEW, Appellant
v.
Anne L. PRECYTHE, Director of the Department of Corrections, et al., Appellees No: 17-3052 United States Court of Appeals, Eighth Circuit. March 15, 2018 Raechel Jean Bimmerle, Robert N. Hochman, SIDLEY & AUSTIN, Chicago, IL, Cheryl Ann Pilate, MORGAN & PILATE, Kansas City, MO, for Plaintiff-Appellant Russell Bucklew, Pro Se. David J. Hansen, Stephen David Hawke, Michael Joseph Spillane, Assistant Attorneys General, Joshua Divine, ATTORNEY GENERAL'S OFFICE, Jefferson City, MO, for Defendants-Appellees. Before WOLLMAN, LOKEN, and COLLOTON, Circuit Judges.

ORDER

Bucklew's motion for stay of execution has been considered by the court and is denied.
